				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: How do people twist more than 3 songs?<a name="73089"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 10 05 2:10 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>in general each song has a cast time of 3 seconds and a duration of 12 seconds so if you cast one every 3 seconds it will loop and youll be casting the first one just as it wears off.  If you twist 5 then you are going to keep droping a song.  you just have to hit the hotkey as soon as the previous song lands.
<br />

<br />
not every song has an icon that shows so you may be doing four songs without realising it.</span></td>
