				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't think there really is a secret.  I can do four with ease and never drop them, depending of course on fizzles or missed notes.
<br />

<br />
Melody seems to work fine with four.  Manually twisting, I found what might be a trick or might be more relevant to my machine/server.  Before the casting bar gets all the way accross, stop it and begin your next twist.  If I wait for it to complete and disappear before I start the next song, I'll never get 4 in.  </span></td>
