				<td colspan="2"><span>As was implied, the secret to twisting more than 3 songs (which I can and do do often, keeping all of them up) is to realize that the song lands before the casting bar disappears.  I am not certain if it is probable for anyone to twist 5 (buff songs) or not, but I wouldn't be too surprised (if they had no lag, no fizzles, and were pretty darn near perfect).  Each server tic last SIX seconds, not three (the easiest way to show this is to hold your mouse over a buff...the time remaining will go down in incriments of six) and since our songs only take 3 seconds to cast, and last for three tics (they show 12 seconds, and last until the tic AFTER they hit zero) it should be possible to twist 5 (if you start RIGHT when a server tic is occours) with minimal drops...prolly doesn't happen too much tho.  </span></td>
			</tr><tr>
