				<td colspan="2"><span>Another option is items with instant cast right clicky songs on them.
<br />

<br />
Lute of Flowing Waters is something i used for a long time. Pre OOW upgrade and /melody i had 1 2 and 3 on my numeric keypad as my standard twist. With the lute i also mapped 0 to activate a hotkey slot that i had draged the lute into. My twist then changed from 112233 to 011022033.
<br />

<br />
Voila 4 song twist. OK OK OK i know its not really a 4 song twist but it always seemed to impress those that were not in the know how i managed to keep 4 songs up permanently for hours at a time.</span></td>
